# ─── Per-user / runtime state (never commit) ─────────────────────────────
# Sprint 05 taste profile, Sprint 06 traces, pre-Sprint-05 legacy file.
# Opt out via VISIONARY_DISABLE_TASTE=1 / VISIONARY_NO_TRACES=1 — see
# docs/taste-privacy.md.
.visionary-cache/
.visionary/
taste/
system.md

# Claude Code agent worktrees — created by isolated subagent dispatch,
# locked while the runtime owns them, removed at session end.
.claude/worktrees/

# Playwright MCP runtime dir (browser contexts / screenshots)
.playwright-mcp/

# Sprint 04 BoN fan-out smoke-test scratch dir — fork-candidate tests
# occasionally seed this; nothing in it is meant to be persisted.
benchmark/.bon-test-cache/

# Per-project visionary-kit (user-curated realism data from /visionary-kit).
# Schema + example ship under skills/visionary/schemas/ and docs/sprints/
# artifacts/; the project's own kit stays local.
/visionary-kit.json

# ─── Internal working docs (do not ship to public remotes) ───────────────
# Maintainer-only analysis briefs and scratch files. Commit-deny by pattern.
Future implementation and fixes.md
*.stackdump
bash.exe.stackdump

# ─── Node / package managers ─────────────────────────────────────────────
node_modules/
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# ─── OS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# ─── Build artifacts ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
dist/
.cache/
*.tmp

# ─── ML model binaries (Sprint 11 DINOv2-small ~22 MB, etc) ──────────────
# Models are lazy-downloaded to ~/.visionary/models/ — repo never carries
# the binaries. Belt-and-suspenders here in case someone misconfigures.
*.onnx
*.gguf
*.safetensors
*.bin
models/*.onnx
models/dinov2-small.onnx
# Anchor screenshots (Sprint 11 build-anchors.mjs input) — kept local for
# size + curation provenance. Only the computed _index.json is shared.
models/style-anchors/*/*.png
models/style-anchors/*/*.jpg
models/style-anchors/*/*.jpeg

# ─── MCP-server runtime (Sprint 10) — host installs deps locally ─────────
packages/mcp-server/node_modules/
packages/*/node_modules/
packages/*/dist/

# ─── Husky generated dirs (Sprint 14) ────────────────────────────────────
# .husky/pre-commit is committed; the _ subdir is regenerated by `npx husky`.
.husky/_/

# ─── Environment ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

# ─── IDE ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# ─── Claude Code local state (per-user, not plugin code) ─────────────────
.claude/
